data.description: NEW FLOORING! LVP & Carpet installed last week. Newer Marvin Windows and patio door. Beautiful open kitchen with breakfast bar and granite counters. Natural wood floor-to-ceiling cabinets with pull-outs, soft-close drawers and undercabinet lighting. Large bedroom closets with built-in storage system. Tubular skylights bring in lots of natural light. Freshly paint with updated bathrooms, tile flooring, lighting and more. Come experience the beauty of the Cimarron Ponds community! Enjoy the natural setting with ponds and paths nestled among mature trees. Have fun at the community pool, pickleball courts and tennis courts. Adjacent to the Luce Line State Trail and close to Parkers Lake Park with tons of amenities. Convenient to shopping and highways.
